texts.text: Bedrock Edition Dev is a beta version of Bedrock Edition 1.16 accessible only by developers and marketplace content creators. It was discovered and leaked by a YouTuber Element X.

This version has additional development features, for example: An F3 Screen, ability to enable on-screen touch screen controls to test them for mobile versions, Advanced developer settings for terrain generation and weather, and ability to slow down the time without needing an add-on.
